Best Formula - HIGH AVAILABILITY - MULTI ZONE DEPLOYMENT



Types of Scaling

Vertical Scaling
    Scale up - increase the capacity of Instances
    Scale Down - decrease the capacity of Instances
Horizontal Scaling
    Scale Out - Increase the number of Instances
    Scale In - Decrease the number of Instances



Auto Scaling Group

 + Replaces unhealthy machine to Healthy one
 + Scale Out if More load needs
 + Scale in if only required less load

 *** RDS Supports only Vertical Scaling *****

